description:
𝐓𝐇𝐈𝐒 𝐌𝐀𝐑𝐂𝐇!

𝐒𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐝𝐚𝐲 𝟕𝐭𝐡 𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐜𝐡, we Return to the vaults, bringing you the sounds of trance and more.

Our last event with Thelma was incredible. The place was rocking from the get go.

We pride ourselves in that TranceParency is just one big party for all. And that’s why we have grown as a wee family, the artists on this lineup are people who have become part of that family, people who we believe to be carrying this scene in Scotland and beyond.

They know exactly how to get you jumping!

Joining us in the capitals favourite club @cab_vol

